r":395},[219,1463,1464,1466,1468,1470,1472,1474,1476,1478,1480],{"class":221,"line":575},[219,1465,402],{"class":342},[219,1467,405],{"class":361},[219,1469,365],{"class":342},[219,1471,832],{"class":229},[219,1473,349],{"class":342},[219,1475,479],{"class":338},[219,1477,839],{"class":482},[219,1479,486],{"class":338},[219,1481,419],{"class":342},[219,1483,1484,1486,1488,1490,1492],{"class":221,"line":860},[219,1485,425],{"class":342},[219,1487,428],{"class":361},[219,1489,365],{"class":342},[219,1491,854],{"class":229},[219,1493,857],{"class":342},[219,1495,1496,1498,1501,1503,1506],{"class":221,"line":865},[219,1497,494],{"class":338},[219,1499,1500],{"class":342}," (message.author.bot) ",[219,1502,512],{"class":338},[219,1504,1505],{"class":342},"; ",[219,1507,1508],{"class":1146},"\u002F\u002F prevent bot-to-bot reply loops\n",[219,1510,1511,1514,1517,1519,1521,1523],{"class":221,"line":870},[219,1512,1513],{"class":338},"  const",[219,1515,1516],{"class":236}," response",[219,1518,381],{"class":338},[219,1520,1068],{"class":338},[219,1522,1037],{"class":361},[219,1524,1525],{"class":342},"(message.content);\n",[219,1527,1528,1531,1533],{"class":221,"line":1131},[219,1529,1530],{"class":342},"  message.",[219,1532,549],{"class":361},[219,1534,1535],{"class":342},"(response);\n",[219,1537,1538],{"class":221,"line":1150},[219,1539,457],{"class":342},[219,1541,1542],{"class":221,"line":1162},[219,1543,396],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":395},[219,1545,1546,1548,1550,1552,1554],{"class":221,"line":1168},[219,1547,402],{"class":342},[219,1549,580],{"class":361},[219,1551,877],{"class":342},[219,1553,880],{"class":236},[219,1555,371],{"class":342},[17,1557,1558,1559,1562],{},"The new piece here is ",[157,1560,1561],{},"message.reply(response);"," — replies to the user's message. Now in Discord, send a message and your bot will reply with what OpenAI returns.",[17,1564,1565],{},[83,1566],{"alt":1567,"src":1568},"JOJO","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F3dJOApu.png",[17,1570,1571],{},[83,1572],{"alt":1567,"src":1573},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F2V0pEpu.png",[12,1575,1577],{"id":1576},"making-your-discord-bot-smarter","Making your Discord Bot smarter",[17,1579,1580],{},"So we've built a Discord chatbot integrated with OpenAI. But it has some weaknesses:",[47,1582,1583,1586],{},[50,1584,1585],{},"Feels a bit dumb",[50,1587,1588],{},"No conversation context",[17,1590,1591],{},"To solve this, we'd need to stack previous messages (including bot replies) and send them all to OpenAI with each new user message — so OpenAI can understand context.",[17,1593,1594,1595,1600],{},"But there's a big problem — OpenAI counts tokens per character, so stacking is expensive. See ",[29,1596,1599],{"href":1597,"rel":1598},"https:\u002F\u002Fjcyh.work\u002Fchatgpt-integration-with-linebot\u002F",[33],"this person's writeup"," for details.",[17,1602,1603],{},"If you still want to make the bot smarter, here's an approach — use Discord's Forum.",[17,1605,1606],{},[83,1607],{"alt":1608,"src":1609},"Forum","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjQ4swB2.png",[17,1611,1612],{},"Forum posts let you gather context for a single topic, then send to OpenAI. You can also limit the total character count per post to limit OpenAI's compute cost.",[17,1614,1615],{},"But Discord Forums require Community mode if I remember correctly. Another option: only fetch a limited number of recent messages — e.g. the last 10 — and reset above that. Less elegant, but it works.",[17,1617,1618],{},"Personally I think Forum mode is still better xD.",[12,1620,1622],{"id":1621},"sample-code","Sample code",[17,1624,1625],{},"Sample code for reference — you can use this post to set up Discord, then use my code to build your own chatbot.",[17,1627,1628,1629],{},"GitHub: ",[29,1630,1631],{"href":1631,"rel":1632},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fhermione",[33],[12,1634,1636],{"id":1635},"updates","Updates",[17,1638,1639],{},"OpenAI later released the ChatGPT API. I updated the sample code — see the commits below to learn how to convert from GPT-3 to GPT-3.5:",[47,1641,1642,1649,1656],{},[50,1643,1644],{},[29,1645,1648],{"href":1646,"rel":1647},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fhermione\u002Fcommit\u002Fccb78b0f5f5b42eb366e5f85f50612a5f31842be",[33],"Switch to createChatCompletion",[50,1650,1651],{},[29,1652,1655],{"href":1653,"rel":1654},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fhermione\u002Fcommit\u002F2a701f7c4335850b9ace40c1511900c7c80aabb7",[33],"Forum mode adjustment",[50,1657,1658],{},[29,1659,1662],{"href":1660,"rel":1661},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fhermione\u002Fcommit\u002F3957938f69e548d0a5ecb03534685861d41cbf19",[33],"Text-string mode adjustment",[17,1664,1665],{},"I've also split branches for the two versions, so you can switch branches to compare.",[12,1667,1669],{"id":1668},"important-notes","Important notes",[17,1671,1672],{},"This post does NOT provide a free OpenAI API Key or Discord Token. You need to apply for your own — this is just an integration example. To run it, get both:",[47,1674,1675,1682],{},[50,1676,1677,1678],{},"OpenAI API Key: ",[29,1679,1680],{"href":1680,"rel":1681},"https:\u002F\u002Fplatform.openai.com\u002F",[33],[50,1683,1684,1685],{},"Discord Token: ",[29,1686,76],{"href":76,"rel":1687},[33],[17,1689,1690,1691,35],{},"For OpenAI Key application steps, see the \"Apply for OpenAI API\" section in ",[29,1692,34],{"href":1693,"rel":1694},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\u002Fodejs\u002F20221210\u002F1224824056\u002F#%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-OpenAI-API",[33],[17,1696,1697,1698,1701],{},"This sample project uses env variables. If you've applied for the keys but still get \"",[157,1699,1700],{},"RequestAbortedError [AbortError]: Request aborted","\" or \"Sorry, I hit a 401 - Unauthorized error\", your Key or Token is wrong — check your .env. Also, the project uses Node.js, so make sure Node.js is installed first.",[17,1703,1704,1705],{},"Bonus — about Env: ",[29,1706,1709],{"href":1707,"rel":1708},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20230218\u002F3618693250\u002F",[33],"What is Env and when should you use it? (article in Mandarin)",[1711,1712,1713],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .smYoP, html code.shiki .smYoP{--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-default:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sWayO, html code.shiki .sWayO{--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-default:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .stw71, html code.shiki .stw71{--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-default:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#91CBFF}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html.dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sOudu, html code.shiki .sOudu{--shiki-light:#D73